[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Daichi. Still doing that Tuesday taiko class? My cousin's kid is looking for a beginner spot in Bellevue, figured you'd know the landscape.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842198.000000",
    "ts": "1766842198.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yeah, three months in now. Still humbling — took me an embarrassingly long time to get the basic strike consistent. Sensei's patient but I can tell.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842258.000000",
    "ts": "1766842258.000000",
    "user_id": "U002KEVIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You flew a 737 MAX recurrent last month and taiko is what's got you grinding 😂",
    "thread_ts": "1766842318.000000",
    "ts": "1766842318.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Completely different skill set, Kevin. The drum doesn't care about your ATP certificate. No partial credit for situational awareness.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842378.000000",
    "ts": "1766842378.000000",
    "user_id": "U002KEVIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Fair point. Is it the Bellevue Community Arts spot on Tuesdays?",
    "thread_ts": "1766842438.000000",
    "ts": "1766842438.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yeah, Tuesday evenings. Tell him to email ahead — fills up fast. Hana's been asking to come watch and honestly I'm not ready for that level of scrutiny from a seven-year-old.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842498.000000",
    "ts": "1766842498.000000",
    "user_id": "U002KEVIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha. Kids are the hardest audience. Worse than a check ride.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842558.000000",
    "ts": "1766842558.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Exactly. She comes when I can finish Miyake without stopping. Targeting winter. Gambatte to me.",
    "thread_ts": "1766842618.000000",
    "ts": "1766842618.000000",
    "user_id": "U002KEVIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "hey you teaching Kenji those drums or is that all you now 😂 heard you've been hitting up taiko class every tuesday",
    "thread_ts": "1766671184.000000",
    "ts": "1766671184.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "beginner class in Bellevue. been going a few weeks. Kenji's more interested in video games right now but I haven't given up on him yet.",
    "thread_ts": "1766671244.000000",
    "ts": "1766671244.000000",
    "user_id": "U003THOMAS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ha that tracks. you any good or still embarrassing yourself up there",
    "thread_ts": "1766671304.000000",
    "ts": "1766671304.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I can hold a basic pattern without the sensei stopping the whole room. that's the bar I set and I'm clearing it.",
    "thread_ts": "1766671364.000000",
    "ts": "1766671364.000000",
    "user_id": "U003THOMAS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "sets the bar real low 😂 what's Aisha think about you coming home beat from drums on top of those 5am Equinox days",
    "thread_ts": "1766671424.000000",
    "ts": "1766671424.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "she said 'at least you're not just watching NHK reruns.' so. support comes in different forms.",
    "thread_ts": "1766671484.000000",
    "ts": "1766671484.000000",
    "user_id": "U003THOMAS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol fair enough. you think it sticks or is this like the cycling thing",
    "thread_ts": "1766671544.000000",
    "ts": "1766671544.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "taiko has better rhythm than cycling. yosh, I'm sticking with it.",
    "thread_ts": "1766671604.000000",
    "ts": "1766671604.000000",
    "user_id": "U003THOMAS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "yo daichi, heard you're back at that taiko thing again tuesday. still in beginner? 😄",
    "thread_ts": "1766736129.000000",
    "ts": "1766736129.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Three semesters, still beginner. Instructor says I have 'pilot hands' — apparently not a compliment.",
    "thread_ts": "1766736189.000000",
    "ts": "1766736189.000000",
    "user_id": "U004RANDY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lmao pilot hands?? what does that even mean",
    "thread_ts": "1766736249.000000",
    "ts": "1766736249.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Too controlled. Taiko wants you to let the beat fall, not place it. Placing it is all I know how to do.",
    "thread_ts": "1766736309.000000",
    "ts": "1766736309.000000",
    "user_id": "U004RANDY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "does aisha ever come watch or is this a solo operation",
    "thread_ts": "1766736369.000000",
    "ts": "1766736369.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Solo. She'd never let me forget the beginner room. Hana already asked why I take class with kids.",
    "thread_ts": "1766736429.000000",
    "ts": "1766736429.000000",
    "user_id": "U004RANDY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "hana roasting you 😂 how old is she now",
    "thread_ts": "1766736489.000000",
    "ts": "1766736489.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Eight. Meaner than any check airman I've flown with. Yosh, she's going somewhere.",
    "thread_ts": "1766736549.000000",
    "ts": "1766736549.000000",
    "user_id": "U004RANDY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Heading to taiko after Hana's pickup today. Six weeks in and sensei says my don strike is 'showing progress.' Very diplomatic woman.",
    "thread_ts": "1766860609.000000",
    "ts": "1766860609.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Beginner taiko AND school pickup on the same day? Respect. How's Hana feel about waiting around for that?",
    "thread_ts": "1766860669.000000",
    "ts": "1766860669.000000",
    "user_id": "U005ROBERT"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "She actually wants to watch. Might let her sit in the back. Either she loves it or I never hear the end of it.",
    "thread_ts": "1766860729.000000",
    "ts": "1766860729.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha. Probably the second one. You on the 7am sim brief tomorrow or did you swap with Torres?",
    "thread_ts": "1766860789.000000",
    "ts": "1766860789.000000",
    "user_id": "U005ROBERT"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "7am. I'll be off the Equinox floor by 6:30, easy. Grab matcha on Bellevue Way and I'm there.",
    "thread_ts": "1766860849.000000",
    "ts": "1766860849.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Of course you will. Some of us don't wake up at 4:45 voluntarily, Mosley.",
    "thread_ts": "1766860909.000000",
    "ts": "1766860909.000000",
    "user_id": "U005ROBERT"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "5am. There's a difference. See you at seven — don't be the guy who shows up to a sim review with no coffee.",
    "thread_ts": "1766860969.000000",
    "ts": "1766860969.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "No promises. Good luck with the wrist snap tonight 🥁",
    "thread_ts": "1766861029.000000",
    "ts": "1766861029.000000",
    "user_id": "U005ROBERT"
  },
